OL,6,F"But after 14 years in Parliament, and
OL,7,Fmultiple roles in Cabinet and
OL,8,FGovernment, I have come to the
OL,9,Fdecision not to stand again at the
OL,10,Fnext general election. Every morning
OL,11,Fas I shave my head in the mirror, I
OL,12,Fhave to pinch myself.
OL,14,F"How is it that a boy from Baghdad who
OL,15,Fcame to these shores, fleeing
OL,16,Fpersecution and unable to speak a word
OL,17,Fof English, was able to do as much as
OL,18,FI have?"
