OL,6,FMr Zahawi was education secretary from
OL,7,FSeptember 2021 to July 2022 and had a
OL,8,Fshort stint as chancellor of the
OL,9,Fexchequer between July and September
OL,10,F2022.
OL,12,FIn 2023, Rishi Sunak sacked Mr Zahawi
OL,13,Fas Tory Party chairman after an ethics
OL,14,Finquiry found he had broken the
OL,15,FMinisterial Code several times over
OL,16,Fhis tax affairs.
